        <updateDate>2020-04-24T14:04:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Universal Charitable Giving Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill allows individual taxpayers a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions even if such taxpayers do not elect to itemize deductions for the taxable year. The deduction may not exceed one-third of the taxpayer's standard deduction amount.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
